{"favorite_id": 10136, "calc_type": "calculator", "dosing": false, "full_title_en": "ABIC Score for Alcoholic Hepatitis", "short_title_en": "ABIC Score for Alcoholic Hepatitis", "medium_description_en": "<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e1968915-7fff-03d6-f4bf-834aed92e040\">Predicts survival in alcoholic hepatitis.</span>", "short_description_en": "Alcohol hepatitis survival.", "before_use": "", "instructions_en": "", "purpose_en": ["Prognosis"], "disease_en": ["Alcoholism", "Drug/Alcohol Use", "Hepatitis"], "specialty_en": ["Hepatology", "Toxicology", "Gastroenterology"], "chief_complaint_en": ["Intoxication/Overdose", "Abdominal Pain"], "system_en": ["Hepatic"], "search_abbreviation_en": ["Alcohol hepatitis", "Alcoholic hepatitis score"], "slug": "abic-score-alcoholic-hepatitis", "seo": {"meta_description_en": "The ABIC Score for Alcoholic Hepatitis predicts survival in alcoholic hepatitis.", "keywords_en": "Alcohol hepatitis, Alcoholic hepatitis score, Glasgow, Lillie model"}, "content": {"how_to_use": {"use_case_en": "<p>Patients with alcoholic hepatitis.</p>", "pearls_pitfalls_en": "", "why_use_en": "<p>Performs similarly to <calculator id=\"56\">Maddrey's Discriminant Function</calculator> at predicting mortality, and better than the <calculator id=\"78\">MELD Score</calculator> and <calculator id=\"2024\">Lille Model</calculator>, in one retrospective study (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/27922027\" target=\"_blank\">Garcia-Saenz-de-Sicilia 2017</a>).</p>"}, "next_steps": {"advice_en": "<p>We are not aware of any&nbsp;guidelines that recommend steroid administration based on ABIC Score, but&nbsp;could be reasonable to consider in the decision given its mortality prediction by severity.</p>", "management_en": "", "critical_actions_en": ""}, "about": {"formula_en": "<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6e327eb7-7fff-bfa3-d440-9ed03c4d6834\">ABIC Score = (<strong>A</strong>ge, years &times; 0.1) + (Serum <strong>B</strong>ilirubin, mg/dL &times; 0.08) + (<strong>I</strong>NR &times; 0.8) +&nbsp;(Serum <strong>C</strong>reatinine, mg/dL &times; 0.3) </span></p>", "more_info_en": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Interpretation:</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"*\" /><col width=\"*\" /><col width=\"*\" /><col width=\"*\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>ABIC Score</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Risk group</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Survival at&nbsp;90 days</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Survival&nbsp;at&nbsp;</strong><strong>1 year</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&lt;6.71</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Low</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">100%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">97.1%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">6.71 to &lt;9.00</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Intermediate</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">70%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">64.3%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ge;9.00</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">High</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">25%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">33.3%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b2c41cf6-7fff-e27d-5755-fa62261ec5f9\"></span><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b2c41cf6-7fff-e27d-5755-fa62261ec5f9\"><br /></span></p>", "evidence_based_medicine_en": "", "references_list": {"Original/Primary Reference": [{"href": "https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18721242", "text": "Dominguez M, Rinc\u00f3n D, Abraldes JG, et al. A new scoring system for prognostic stratification of patients with alcoholic hepatitis. Am J Gastroenterol. 2008;103(11):2747-56."}], "Other References": [{"href": "", "text": ""}], "Validation": [{"href": "https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/apt.12654", "text": "Papastergiou V, Tsochatzis EA, Pieri G, et al. Nine scoring models for short-term mortality in alcoholic hepatitis: cross-validation in a biopsy-proven cohort. Aliment Pharmacol Ther. 2014;39(7):721-